1.title: Episode #1.1

episode of.title: My Life in Venice Beach (TV Series 2014– )

1.plot: Right after landing at LAX, Isa's luggage gets stolen and she is off to a rocky start in Hollywood. Good thing everyone at her new home is willing to help her out. Well, almost everyone.

2.title: Episode #1.2

episode of.title: My Life in Venice Beach (TV Series 2014– )

2.plot: Tension grows in the house. Vicky wants Isa out, because she doesn't trust Alex with her around. Isa finds shelter in Larissa's van and Tom lands her a job as a waitress at a well known restaurant. Meanwhile Steffi gets bad news from her immigration lawyer.

3.title: Episode #1.3

episode of.title: My Life in Venice Beach (TV Series 2014– )

3.plot: Vicky looses her model for an important bikini shoot last minute. Dana agrees to help out, but her and Alex get into a fight on set. The two share a history that none of the house mates know about. Isa sees Larissa accepting money from her biker boyfriend Ronny in exchange for a dubious backpack. Is Larissa involved with drugs? Tom once again disappoints Isa when he promises her to pull some strings for a nice hotel room. Once she gets there though, nobody knows of a Tom and there is no room reserved. What is Tom's deal?

4.title: Episode #1.4

episode of.title: My Life in Venice Beach (TV Series 2014– )

4.plot: Finally Larissa & Jayz get closer, when he confesses to her that he has feelings that go beyond a friendship. Vicky pulls off a rather different presentation of her new bikini line, leaving her boss annoyed, but the CEO of a big fashion label intrigued. But is he interested in her work or does he want more? Dana faces Alex, tells him off and moves out of the house for good. Steffi finally lands the audition for a national commercial, but walks off set once she figures out what she would be promoting. Gaby goes on a great date with Pepe, but soon finds out about ...

5.title: Episode #1.5

episode of.title: My Life in Venice Beach (TV Series 2014– )

5.plot: Is Vicky going too far with her new boss? Will Jayz & Larissa get a shot at a real relationship? Is Tom just a typical Los Angeles flake? Will Gaby go to Santa Barbara with Pepe or will his daughter put a stop to their new found romance? Will Isa stay in LA or go back to Germany and does meeting the Hollywood star Brendan Coughlin help solving Steffi's visa issues? All these questions will be answered in this epic mid season finale.

imdb.plot outline: My Life in Venice Beach is a new TV drama that centers around young, German girl Isa who comes to Los Angeles to follow her dream of being a famous singer. She learns quickly that Hollywood isn't as glamorous as it seems and making it big in the city of angels is hard work.
